These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, zombie
There are 2 different nationalities: spanish, nigerian
1. the person watching documentary movies is not to the left of the spanish##8
2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Beverage         | milk   | fanta |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | zombie    |
| Nationality     | spanish  | nigerian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, spy
There are 2 different nationalities: american, spanish
2 different pets are kept: pony, lizard
1. the person watching fantasy movies is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the pony is not to the right of the american##8
3. the american is somewhere to the left of the person watching fantasy movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Movie-Genre      | spy    | fantasy    |
| Nationality   | american | spanish    |
| Pet     | pony  | lizard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, water
House: modern, victorian
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: begonia, balloon-flower
1. the person drinking fanta is not to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##8
2. the victorian house is not the person who growsballoon-flower##6
3. the modern house is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |        2        |
| Beverage      | fanta   | water           |
| House           | modern | victorian |
| Flower   | balloon-flower  | begonia      |

