.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-7::.
City: paris, san-francisco
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey
There are 2 different favourite colors: fuchsia, purple
1. the person who likes fuchsia is not to the right of the person traveling to paris##8
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the right of the person who likes purple##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |
| City        | san-francisco | paris      |
| Sport       | cricket     | ice-hockey |
| Color   | purple        | fuchsia |

