There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, lemonade
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, motorbike
1. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person driving the car##1
3. the person playing canasta is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |  2   |
| Game        | canasta | snooker |
| Beverage         | lemonade     | iced-tea |
| Transport   | motorbike   | car  |

